Download the linux kernel version : linux-4.18.14 

or
 
you can find the version which one you need in this link : www.kernel.org

or

use this commend to download in the terminal : 

wget https://mirrors.edge.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v4.x/linux-4.18.14.tar.xz (just change the verison to what you need)
(get into the "/usr/src" then use the above command)

like :
{
cd /usr/src
wget https://mirrors.edge.kernel.org/pub/linux/kernel/v4.x/linux-4.18.14.tar.xz
}
